      "message": "I definitely remember this actually being necessary at some point; I used a Setting instead of a raw literal specifically to keep the values from getting baked in before we were ready to do so.\n\nBut after digging through things... I agree that it appears things have changed since I initially wrote this code and this now seems to be pointless.",
